{"tid":1035394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"咖哩神童彈鋼琴 速度快到讓人目瞪口呆","createTime":"2019-02-24T14:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T16:56:46.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bf4a3ee68668369c0a7fefbe1909cc5f26fb917f","tid":1035394,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:56:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/JKCorden/status/1093956164620972032\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJKCorden%2Fstatus%2F1093956164620972032&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=1ed071f8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJKCorden%2Fstatus%2F1093956164620972032&h=7d1e743d\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JKCorden/status/1093956164620972032</a><br />\n<br />\n印度12歲男童納達斯瓦蘭（Lydian Nadhaswaram）有音樂上的天賦，能彈一手既快又好的鋼琴。他最近在美國選秀節目中一展身手，讓評審與觀眾看得目瞪口呆。<br />\n<br />\n納達斯瓦蘭來自印度東南部的城市清奈（Chennai），幾年前便以其在鋼琴上的造詣而在印度成名。他在本月播映的美國才藝競賽節目《世界最強》（The World&rsquo;s Best）中演奏經典名曲《大黃蜂的飛行》（Flight of the Bumblebee），結果一炮而紅。<br />\n<br />\n《大黃蜂的飛行》是俄羅斯作曲家林姆斯基-高沙可夫（Nikolai Rimsky-Korsakov）為其歌劇《沙皇薩爾坦的故事》（The Tale of Tsar Saltan）所譜寫的曲子，素以高難度著稱。當這首曲子以很快的速度演奏時，它聽起來就像大黃蜂振翅飛行的嗡嗡聲。<br />\n<br />\n在本次節目中，納達斯瓦蘭先以節拍器每分鐘響160下的正常速度演奏《大黃蜂的飛行》，隨後增加速度至每分鐘208下再演奏一次。當現場評審與觀眾都感到十分驚訝時，他竟然還能再加碼，挑戰每分鐘325下，最終讓眾人佩服不已。<br />\n<br />\n該節目主持人柯登（James Corden）在推特上分享了納達斯瓦蘭表演的影片。他在推文中寫道：「這真的是我在現場看過最好的表演之一。」<br />\n<br />\n    This is genuinely one of the best things I&rsquo;ve ever seen live.<br />\n<a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/FY5LH6vxfI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FFY5LH6vxfI&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=2a4d26ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://pic.twitter.com/FY5LH6vxfI</a><br />\n<br />\n    &mdash; James Corden (@JKCorden) 2019年2月8日<br />\n<br />\n納達斯瓦蘭的精采表演也受到印度同胞和觀眾的讚賞，其中包括演員和運動明星等。<br />\n<br />\n《世界最強》是美國哥倫比亞廣播公司（CBS）在2月剛推出的競賽節目。每個參賽項目由三位主要的評審以及一個由不同領域的50名專家所組成的國際小組進行評分。在初賽中，參賽者必須獲得75分以上，才能晉級下一場比賽。"},{"pid":"02e96d990e228e0bbf3de9638ed84fa2828c556a","tid":1035394,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:58:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/635rQcsdRWo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F635rQcsdRWo&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=d7233839\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/635rQcsdRWo</a>"},{"pid":"e6c0eaf5fd87c1504154dc6813418318537c55f8","tid":1035394,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:59:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_G1ibYMjlHM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D_G1ibYMjlHM&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=36b07e54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_G1ibYMjlHM</a>"},{"pid":"e1dfe9efbe7a7e3179cb01faab3a9280574cb3f7","tid":1035394,"uid":118455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T15:56:17.000Z","msg":"呢d真係天才黎"},{"pid":"c9293b6c202253a8a14fe9bc50fd4bf85b34e9cc","tid":1035394,"uid":182499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:22:21.000Z","msg":"印度仔開外掛"},{"pid":"1149cd63573427803795fa22d4003bff61be3012","tid":1035394,"uid":13303,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:33:26.000Z","msg":"手速咁快第日無女都唔驚"},{"pid":"4ab7611e53760ff80ab3f2dd8b7f4ffd82dd3d43","tid":1035394,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T16:38:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/G7VUFOQ4a5k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FG7VUFOQ4a5k&d=NJeO18TDpfQgexRQIuB%2FGPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=06e345e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/G7VUFOQ4a5k</a><br />\n<br />\n印度人最鐘意開外掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dab8739f75719b4632b76abd1f9f8acd79d3157","tid":1035394,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quot